Package eu.unite.challenge.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FileFormatException
    Exception which is thrown when the input file is empty, or is larger than some value specified in the ConstraintRules class.
    FormatException
    Superclass for various exceptions corresponding to malformed problems
    ItemException
    Exception which is thrown when a line of the input file is malformed.
    LineFormatException
    Exception which is thrown when an item on a specific line is malformed.
    OutOfRangeProblemSizeException
    Exception that is thrown if the problem instance is greater than some value specified in the ConstraintRules class.
